---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2026-03-22';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | DayDreamHub" description="Terms of Service for DayDreamHub - day-use hotel booking platform.">

  <section class="bg-teal-50 py-14 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 prose prose-sm sm:prose text-gray-700 space-y-8">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using DayDreamHub ("the Platform"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Platform.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>DayDreamHub is an online travel agency (OTA) that connects travelers with hotels and properties offering day-use and short-stay plans. We facilitate bookings between guests and property owners but are not directly responsible for the accommodation services provided.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">3. Day-Use Service Terms</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Check-in and check-out must occur on the same calendar day.</li>
          <li>Plans specify available time windows; guests must arrive within the designated check-in period.</li>
          <li>Late arrival beyond the check-in window may result in denied entry at the property's discretion.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">4. Booking Approval Process</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Bookings are subject to hotel owner approval after payment.</li>
          <li>Payment is captured at the time of booking request.</li>
          <li>If the owner declines, a full refund will be processed within 5-10 business days via PayPal.</li>
          <li>DayDreamHub uses a reservation request system. Approval is at the discretion of the property owner.</li>
          <li>You must provide accurate personal information (name, email, phone number) when making a reservation.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">5. No-Show Policy</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Failure to arrive without cancellation will be recorded as a no-show.</li>
          <li>No-show bookings are non-refundable unless the hotel's plan specifies otherwise.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">6. Payment & Platform Fees</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Plans marked as "Prepayment" require payment via PayPal before the reservation request is submitted.</li>
          <li>Plans marked as "Onsite Payment" are paid directly at the property during check-in.</li>
          <li>DayDreamHub charges a service fee included in the displayed price.</li>
          <li>No additional fees are charged to guests at the property.</li>
          <li>DayDreamHub is not responsible for disputes between guests and properties regarding onsite payments.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">7. Age Restriction</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Users must be 18 years or older to make bookings.</li>
          <li>Some properties may have additional age requirements.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">8. Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>Cancellation policies vary by property. Please review each property's specific cancellation policy before making a reservation. DayDreamHub enforces the cancellation policy set by each individual property.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">9. User Accounts</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>An account may be created automatically when you submit a reservation request.</li>
          <li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.</li>
          <li>To request account deletion, contact <a href="mailto:customer@daydreamhub.com" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline">customer@daydreamhub.com</a>. Active reservations will be cancelled upon deletion.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>DayDreamHub acts as an intermediary between guests and properties. We are not liable for any damages, losses, or disputes arising from the accommodation services provided by listed properties. Our liability is limited to the fees collected through the Platform.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">11. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on DayDreamHub, including text, graphics, logos, and software, is the property of DayDreamHub and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>DayDreamHub reserves the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Continued use of the Platform after changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">13. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at <a href="mailto:customer@daydreamhub.com" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline">customer@daydreamhub.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
